Package: fileTypeAnalyzer
Title: Analyzing Files by Their Type
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Jared", "Lander", email = "packages@jaredlander.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The 'fileTypeAnalyzer' package provides tools for analyzing files 
    in a directory by their type. It calculates metrics such as the average number 
    of lines for each file type and can create plots of these metrics. 
    Currently supported file types for analysis include but are not limited to 
    'txt', 'csv', 'R', etc. Custom file types can also be specified by the user.
